Three things to do now:
01
Run the recruiter search on yourself.
Open LinkedIn. Search the job title you
want. Apply the filters a recruiter would.
Would you show up on page one? Page
three? At all? 
Rewrite your headline. Today.
Use the formula. Make it searchable,
not poetic. Recruiters reward precision,
not creativity. Every word is inventory.
03
Reverse-engineer 3 job descriptions.
Pull 3 listings for your target role.
Copy every recurring keyword. Audit
your profile against that list. The gaps
are your playbook.
